What can I help you with today? Whether it's coding, research, system configuration, or just brainstorming, I'm ready to go!"},{"role":"user","content":"okay for access modes, first of all we always dont need to pick it at the start of chat, it should be asked only when necesssary, like when agent has to read a fiel or edit a file etc, normla conversations dont reauire access modes right?

for session metrics , make sure the subagent metrics are accumulated in the session aswell and not just the chat data. which inlcudes tool calls and sub agent tool calls and reasoning etc.

and subagent should have their own tabs which showcase what they are upto.

approvla guard also should be of value not just a showcase.

also chat mode, plan,edit and yolo should be changable mid chat at any point and agent can also suggest chaning it based on what it is wanting to do, it should usggest with reasoning to the user.

and pls make sure the UI you are making is sleek and elegant .

the plan tab on console should be auto scrollable.

the appended text inserted in the chat on each updated tool call should also be in a new line instead of continue paragraphs for cleaner UI UX.

the chat box should return to default size after user sends the prompt.

for tts, have a audio mode, a mute mode and a disbaled mode. 

also for the plan tab, rename it to reasoning tab, for past reasonings, collapse them, only show current reasoning and make sure it ato scrolls aswell.

after you make the changes and test, dont build or restart the server, let me do that bcz your service will crash and you wont be able to continue. pause when you need me to rebuild and restart and then i can prmpt you again when thats done"},{"role":"user","content":"done the rebuild, your last response did not get stored in the chat histroy tho, also the chat modes can be a collapse expand accordian with arrow instead of icons for cleaner look.

the reasoning tabl ui accordians also look broken, very bugged it seems. also i would want monocrhromatic icons instead of these colored unprofessional ones"},{"role":"assistant","content":"Let me look at the current state and fix all these issues.I see the issues. Let me fix three things: the mode switcher (accordion with arrows), the reasoning tab (buggy accordions), and make all icons monochromatic.Now add the `showModeMenu` state and ensure ChevronDown is imported:Now fix the reasoning tab — past entries should be collapsed by default:Now let me make the icons monochromatic across the key panels. First the MetricsPanel:Now update SectionHeader to accept ReactNode icon:Now let me update the right panel tab icons to be monochrome:Now let me fix the mode badge above the chat that uses emoji icons:Now let me also check the SettingsPanel for colored emojis:","tools":[{"id":"call_00_88lqThy7Bm4MHKRVFSMh4992","name":"read","status":"done","result":{"content":[{"type":"text","text":""use client";

import React, { useEffect, useRef, useState } from "react";
import { Loader2, ChevronDown, ChevronRight, Brain } from "lucide-react";

/**
 * ReasoningTab — Shows current live reasoning with auto-scroll.
 * Past reasoning entries are collapsed; only the current one is fully visible.
 */
export default function ExecutionPlan({ executionPlan, reasoningHistory = [] }) {
  const scrollRef = useRef(null);
  const [collapsed, setCollapsed] = useState({});

  // Auto-scroll to bottom when new reasoning content arrives
  useEffect(() => {
    if (scrollRef.current) {
      scrollRef.current.scrollTop = scrollRef.current.scrollHeight;
    }
  }, [executionPlan]);

  const toggleCollapse = (idx) => {
    setCollapsed(prev => ({ ...prev, [idx]: !prev[idx] }));
  };

  // If we have reasoning history entries, show them collapsed with only current expanded
  if (reasoningHistory && reasoningHistory.length > 0) {
    return (
      <div style={{ display: "flex", flexDirection: "column", gap: "10px", height: "100%" }}>
        <div style={{
          fontSize: "0.75rem", fontWeight: "700", color: "var(--text-muted)",
          textTransform: "uppercase", letterSpacing: "0.5px", marginBottom: "4px",
          display: "flex", alignItems: "center", gap: "6px"
        }}>
          <Brain size={14} /> Reasoning Trail
        </div>
        <div
          ref={scrollRef}
          className="reasoning-scroll"
          style={{
            flex: "1",
            display: "flex",
            flexDirection: "column",
            gap: "8px",
            paddingRight: "4px",
            minHeight: 0
          }}
        >
          {reasoningHistory.map((entry, idx) => {
            const isCurrent = idx === reasoningHistory.length - 1;
            const isCollapsed = collapsed[idx] === true;
            const showContent = isCurrent || !isCollapsed;

            return (
              <div
                key={idx}
                style={{
                  border: isCurrent
                    ? "1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3)"
                    : "1px solid var(--border-color)",
                  borderRadius: "8px",
                  background: isCurrent
                    ? "rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.04)"
                    : "rgba(255,255,255,0.015)",
                  overflow: "hidden",
                  transition: "all 0.15s ease"
                }}
              >
                {/* Header */}
                <div
                  onClick={() => { if (!isCurrent) toggleCollapse(idx); }}
                  style={{
                    display: "flex",
                    alignItems: "center",
                    justifyContent: "space-between",
                    padding: "8px 12px",
                    cursor: isCurrent ? "default" : "pointer",
                    userSelect: "none",
                    borderBottom: showContent ? "1px solid var(--border-color)" : "none",
                    background: isCurrent ? "rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.06)" : "transparent"
                  }}
                >
                  <div style={{ display: "flex", alignItems: "center", gap: "6px" }}>
                    <span style={{
                      width: "6px", height: "6px", borderRadius: "50%",
                      background: isCurrent ? "#3b82f6" : "var(--text-dark)",
                      boxShadow: isCurrent ? "0 0 8px #3b82f6" : "none",
                      flexShrink: 0
                    }} />
                    <span style={{
                      fontSize: "0.75rem", fontWeight: isCurrent ? "700" : "500",
                      color: isCurrent ? "#60a5fa" : "var(--text-muted)"
                    }}>
                      {isCurrent ? "● Current Reasoning" : `Past Reasoning #${idx + 1}`}
                    </span>
                    <span style={{ fontSize: "0.65rem", color: "var(--text-dark)" }}>
                      {entry.timestamp || ""}
                    </span>
                  </div>
                  {!isCurrent && (
                    <div style={{ color: "var(--text-muted)" }}>
                      {isCollapsed ? <ChevronRight size={14} /> : <ChevronDown size={14} />}
                    </div>
                  )}
                </div>

                {/* Content */}
                {showContent && (
                  <div
                    className="reasoning-scroll"
                    style={{
                      padding: "10px 12px",
                      fontSize: "0.8rem",
                      color: "var(--text-main)",
                      whiteSpace: "pre-wrap",
                      lineHeight: "1.5",
                      maxHeight: isCurrent ? "none" : "150px",
                      overflowY: isCurrent ? "visible" : "auto",
                      fontFamily: isCurrent ? "inherit" : "ui-monospace, monospace"
                    }}
                  >
                    {entry.content || executionPlan || "No reasoning data yet."}
                  </div>
                )}
              </div>
            );
          })}
        </div>
      </div>
    );
  }

  // Fallback: single-entry view (backward compatible)
  if (!executionPlan) {
    return (
      <div
        style={{
          display: "flex",
          flexDirection: "column",
          alignItems: "center",
          justifyContent: "center",
          height: "100%",
          color: "var(--text-muted)",
          gap: "10px",
          minHeight: "150px",
        }}
      >
        <Loader2 className="animate-spin" style={{ width: "20px", height: "20px" }} />
        <span style={{ fontSize: "0.8rem" }}>Waiting for reasoning...</span>
      </div>
    );
  }

  return (
    <div style={{ display: "flex", flexDirection: "column", gap: "10px", height: "100%" }}>
      <div style={{
        fontSize: "0.75rem", fontWeight: "700", color: "var(--text-muted)",
        textTransform: "uppercase", letterSpacing: "0.5px", marginBottom: "4px",
        display: "flex", alignItems: "center", gap: "6px"
      }}>
        <Brain size={14} /> Current Reasoning
      </div>
      <div
        ref={scrollRef}
        className="reasoning-scroll"
        style={{
          flex: "1",
          fontSize: "0.8rem",
          color: "var(--text-main)",
          whiteSpace: "pre-wrap",
          lineHeight: "1.5",
          padding: "12px",
          background: "rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.03)",
          border: "1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2)",
          borderRadius: "8px",
          minHeight: 0
        }}
      >
        {executionPlan}
      </div>
    </div>
  );
}
"}]}},{"id":"call_00_9sv801o26mNlzwCd7HID2836","name":"edit","status":"done","result":{"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in /home/blanco/builds/LLM-OS-AGENT/dashboard/src/app/page.js."}],"details":{"diff":"      ...
